{"tid":635412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無限遐想！周子瑜「男友襯衫」曬辣腿　集清純性感於一身","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T11:21:48.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2e95271bf4488905e52927bfed0a2113b4bf810f","tid":635412,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5a3e57d1e261ff273932a005_201712232119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5a3e57d1e261ff273932a005_201712232119.png&h=21f1a80b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜在台韓都有不少死忠粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n南韓人氣女團「TWICE」的台灣團員周子瑜，今（20）日與團員現身KBS電視台錄影，周子瑜紮起馬尾，身穿一件OVERSIZE的「男友襯衫」亮相，露出修長細腿，由於襯衫下襬遮住臀部，讓周子瑜乍看之下就像沒穿褲子，集清純與性感於一身的她，讓粉絲有無限遐想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5ad9759aa402303d5b043d2d_201804201307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5ad9759aa402303d5b043d2d_201804201307.jpg&h=252a8a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜比出愛心手指，模樣可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5ad974e8374b722ecd4522f5_201804201304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5ad974e8374b722ecd4522f5_201804201304.jpg&h=5c7c88db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜身穿襯衫的模樣被網友拍下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5ad97563f296ad0244a3a943_201804201306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5ad97563f296ad0244a3a943_201804201306.jpg&h=212e5af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周子瑜在團體中的人氣頗高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/141152_ef508887b5285e2ed061379e78e2eef4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F141152_ef508887b5285e2ed061379e78e2eef4.png&h=31ff843e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「TWICE」在4月初發行的迷你專輯《What is Love?》，同名主打歌上架不到一小時就登上韓國最大音源網站Melon及13個國家的iTunes冠軍，專輯預購量更突破35萬張，最近她們也勤跑通告宣傳，人氣爆表！"},{"pid":"e06be7ee08c18451351d9ef62856bf2f70b7ed5d","tid":635412,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6741f28d9db12ec188cd48ba2339456088b11bed","tid":635412,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"0b1f2e0ac7a8d511d1a0dcce5d3966e63710db98","tid":635412,"uid":6683,"like":16,"dislike":20,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"條腿粗過車呔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57dc8280960a0c5dc537da3209abe91b1bf3791","tid":635412,"uid":53399,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1f2e0ac7a8d511d1a0dcce5d3966e63710db98","tid":635412,"uid":6683,"like":16,"dislike":20,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"條腿粗過車呔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"你鍾意頂骨頭"},{"pid":"0135e0a149f176f314a37192675dc87d91c3c1fd","tid":635412,"uid":38988,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e57dc8280960a0c5dc537da3209abe91b1bf3791","tid":635412,"uid":53399,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1f2e0ac7a8d511d